      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     rea-100
                     rea-200
                     rea-300
                     rea-400
                     rea-500
                     rea-600
                     rea-700
                     rea-800
                     depending            on   z-key                  .
       rea-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Read per chiave indice 1                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        z-lok                =    1
                     go to rea-110.
      *                     *------------------------------------------*
      *                     * Read no lock                             *
      *                     *------------------------------------------*
           read      fil    with no lock
                            key  is fil-k01
                            invalid key
                            go to   rea-990.
           go to     rea-980.
       rea-110.
      *                     *------------------------------------------*
      *                     * Read with lock                           *
      *                     *------------------------------------------*
           read      fil    key  is fil-k01
                            invalid key
                            go to   rea-990.
           go to     rea-980.
       rea-200.
